            "detailed_description": "<img src=\"https://steamcdn-a.akamaihd.net/steam/apps/414340/extras/BAFTA_Steam_MAIN.jpg?t=1548760394\" ><br><br>From the makers of Heavenly Sword, Enslaved: Odyssey to the West, and DmC: Devil May Cry, comes a warrior’s brutal journey into myth and madness.<br><br>Set in the Viking age, a broken Celtic warrior embarks on a haunting vision quest into Viking Hell to fight for the soul of her dead lover. <br><br>Created in collaboration with neuroscientists and people who experience psychosis, Hellblade: Senua’s Sacrifice will pull you deep into Senua’s mind.<br><br><img src=\"https://steamcdn-a.akamaihd.net/steam/apps/414340/extras/Steam_gameawards.jpg?t=1548760394\" ><br><br><img src=\"https://steamcdn-a.akamaihd.net/steam/apps/414340/extras/HBAccolades_steam.jpg?t=1548760394\" >",
